==
== Subject:     Multiple Heap Overflows Allow Remote
==              Code Execution
== CVE ID#:     CVE-2007-2446
==
== Versions:    Samba 3.0.0 - 3.0.25rc3 (inclusive)
==
== Summary:     Various bugs in Samba's NDR parsing
==              can allow a user to send specially
